Package: Beziervizer
Title: An R package for plotting interactive Bezier curves
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Ziyan", "Xiong",email = "zyxiong@tamu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides functions for plotting interactive bezier curves. Users can adjust various parameters in the plotted reuslts and see how the Bezier curve will change according to the change in each parameter. 
